  {
    "hotel_id": "782823",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hakata-green-hotel-building-no-1/hotel/fukuoka-jp.html",
    "name": "Hakata Green Hotel Building No.1",
    "detail": "I booked this hotel at the last minute, so there weren't a lot of other options available that were in my preferred price range. Fortunately, Hakata Green Hotel turned out to be a really great experience. The hotel was right next to Hakata Station, which is only two stops from Fukuoka Airport. I was a little confused by the directions I got from Google Maps because I arrived at the place that is marked on the map and it turned out to be Building No. 2, and then there's an Annex. Building No. 1. is part of the complex, though, so once I realized that it was all on the same block, I had no trouble finding the hotel. I'm not sure how much English support the staff is able to provide, but my simple Japanese was good enough to get by. Check in was quick and easy, and the room was clean and comfortable with good facilities. I slept like a baby on the comfortable bed, and then I had breakfast at the buffet on the bottom floor the next morning. Most of the dishes were European, but there were some Japanese style breakfast items to choose as well, and the coffee was delicious. Overall, I felt like the quality was just right for the price, and I would stay here again.",
